sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor Instructor
participant GradeConsole
participant GradeService
participant GradeRepository
participant GradeJson as grades.json

== Update Grade ==
Instructor->>GradeConsole: Select "Update Grade"
GradeConsole->>Instructor: Prompt for student ID and new grade
Instructor-->>GradeConsole: studentId, newGrade
GradeConsole->>GradeService: updateGrade(studentId, newGrade)
GradeService->>GradeService: findStudentById(studentId)
GradeService->>GradeService: isValidGrade(newGrade)
alt valid ID and grade in allowed range
  GradeService->>GradeService: replace stored grade
  GradeService-->>GradeConsole: update success
  GradeConsole->>GradeService: getAllStudents()
  GradeService-->>GradeConsole: students
  GradeConsole->>GradeRepository: saveStudents(students)
  GradeRepository->>GradeJson: write updated students array
  GradeJson-->>GradeRepository: persisted
  GradeRepository-->>GradeConsole: save complete
  GradeConsole-->>Instructor: Display success
else invalid ID or invalid grade
  GradeService-->>GradeConsole: update failure
  GradeConsole-->>Instructor: Display validation error
end
